# standings
A JavaScript driven web page to display possible NBA standings
based on converted conferences. Online at:
                                   http://convertnbatk.000webhostapp.com 

To use locally, simply pull and visit index.html

Run python/get_standings.py to update standings after official
NBA games

Run python/create_new_confs.py to yield the conversions json file,
new_confs.json

Adjust the conferences in python/create_new_confs.py and change
conference_names in showSiteCustom() function of js/which.js, if
you would like to change the primary converted conferences.
